'''空氣栓塞'''（air embolism）是指[[氣體|氣體]]形成[[氣泡|氣泡]]進入[[循环系统|循环系统]]中，空氣栓塞屬於[[栓子|栓子]]（血液中游離的固體，液體或氣體團塊），[[潛水|潛水]]意外可能造成空氣栓塞，也有一些因為醫源性的處置造成<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tsim.org.tw/journal/jour20-4/04.PDF |title=動脈氣體栓塞症 |access-date=2016-05-25 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305014858/http://www.tsim.org.tw/journal/jour20-4/04.PDF |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==症狀和體徵==
[[File:Echokardiographiebefund_einer_Luftembolie.webm|thumb]]之後，經過胃部的{{le|胰腺假性囊肿|pancreatic pseudocyst}}穿刺後，出現的空氣栓塞]]
動脈空氣栓塞可能會出現症狀，但也可能因其他環境因素所忽略，例如低溫症，或是因為其他明顯原因造成的疼痛。若懷疑是肺過度擴張損傷，建議進行神經檢查<ref name="USNDM R6" >{{cite book |title=US Navy Diving Manual, 6th revision |year=2006 |publisher=US Naval Sea Systems Command |location=United States |url=http://www.supsalv.org/00c3_publications.asp?destPage=00c3&pageID=3.9 |accessdate=2008-06-15 |author=US Navy |archive-date=2008-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502023541/http://www.supsalv.org/00c3_publications.asp?destPage=00c3&pageId=3.9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。潛水後的[[減壓症|減壓症]]症狀很類似動脈空氣栓塞，而且常常造成混淆，不過兩者的處理方式大致類似。

症狀包括<ref name="USNDM R6" />：
*意識喪失（昏迷）
*呼吸停止
*眩暈
*驚厥
*震顫
*身體無法協調
*身體部份機能無法控制
*身體麻木或麻痺
*非常疲​​勞
*四肢虛弱
*身體部份區域感覺異常
*視覺異常或聽力異常
*性格改變
*認知障礙
*噁心或嘔吐
*血痰
<!--*Symptoms of other consequences of lung overexpansion such as pneumothorax, subcutaneous or mediastinal emphysema may also be present.-->

若針對受傷的潛水員，很難區分動脈空氣栓塞及減壓症，而二者也可能同時出現。許多例子中，個人潜水历史有助於排除減壓症，若有其他肺過度擴張損傷的症狀，就更可能是發生空氣栓塞。

==成因==
在手術或是醫療處理（例如[[輸液|輸液]]）中，可能會有少量的空氣進入血液循環中（例如氣泡進入輸液管中），不過大部份這類的空氣栓塞都是在靜脈，而且會在肺部停下來不會繼續流動，因此會造成[[症狀|症狀]]的靜脈空氣栓塞相當少見<ref name="Emby 2012" >{{cite journal|author1=Emby, DJ|author2=Ho, K|title=Air embolus revisited – a diagnostic and interventional radiological perspective (bubble trouble and the dynamic Mercedes Benz sign)|url=http://www.ajol.info/index.php/sajr/article/viewFile/34461/6388|journal=African Journals Online|date=March 2006|volume=10|issue=1|pages=3–7|doi=10.4102/sajr.v10i1.186|access-date=2016-05-26|archive-date=2019-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117113927/https://www.ajol.info//index.php/sajr/article/viewFile/34461/6388|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

靜脈空氣栓塞中，若有大的氣泡堵在心臟，使血液無法由右[[心室|心室]]流到肺部，可能會造成死亡<ref name=CMBI>{{cite web |url=http://cmbi.bjmu.edu.cn/uptodate/critical%20care/embolic%20disease/air%20embolism.htm |title=Air Embolism |author=Liza C O'Dowd(MD), Mark A Kelley (MD) |publisher=Chinese Medical & Biological Informatics |accessdate=2011-05-11 |archive-date=2011-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717210438/http://cmbi.bjmu.edu.cn/uptodate/critical%20care/embolic%20disease/air%20embolism.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=uhms>{{cite web |url=http://www.uhms.org/ResourceLibrary/Indications/AirorGasEmbolism/tabid/271/Default.aspx |title=Air or Gas Embolism |author=Undersea and Hyperbaric Medical Society |accessdate=2008-05-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080502191923/http://www.uhms.org/ResourceLibrary/Indications/AirorGasEmbolism/tabid/271/Default.aspx |archivedate=2008年5月2日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。不過在[[動物實驗|動物實驗]]中發現，會造成死亡的靜脈空氣栓塞氣體量會隨許多因素而不同<ref>{{cite journal|last1=van Hulst|first1=RA|last2=Klein|first2=J|last3=Lachmann|first3=B|title=Gas embolism: pathophysiology and treatment.|journal=Clinical physiology and functional imaging|date=September 2003|volume=23|issue=5|pages=237–46|pmid=12950319|doi=10.1046/j.1475-097x.2003.00505.x}}</ref>。若是針對人類的情形，若靜脈中注射超過100mL的空氣。且注射速率超過100 mL/s，可能會致命<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Platz|first1=E|title=Tangential gunshot wound to the chest causing venous air embolism: a case report and review.|journal=The Journal of emergency medicine|date=August 2011|volume=41|issue=2|pages=e25-9|doi=10.1016/j.jemermed.2008.01.023|pmid=18799282}}</ref>。若是深度潛水的快速降壓，或是减压事故，會出現大量的，會造成症狀的靜脈空氣栓塞，也會影響血液在肺部的流動，造成呼吸窘迫及[[缺氧|缺氧]]<ref name=emr474 />。

若空氣栓塞出現在動脈，稱為動脈空氣栓塞（arterial gas embolism，AGE）。動脈空氣栓塞比靜脈空氣栓塞要嚴重的多，因為會直接影響身體某個部位的供血。動脈空氣栓塞的症狀和其影響供血的部位有關，若影響到大腦或是心臟，也可能造成[[中風|中風]]或是[[心肌梗死|心肌梗死]]<ref name=emr474 />。隨著部位不同，會產生動脈空氣栓塞症狀的氣體量也會不同，在腦血管2 mL的空氣就可以致命，而在冠狀動脈中，0.5 mL的空氣就會造成心搏停止<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ho|first1=AM|title=Is emergency thoracotomy always the most appropriate immediate intervention for systemic air embolism after lung trauma?|journal=Chest|date=July 1999|volume=116|issue=1|pages=234–7|pmid=10424531|url=http://journal.publications.chestnet.org/data/Journals/CHEST/21927/234.pdf|doi=10.1378/chest.116.1.234}}</ref><ref>{{EMedicine|article|761367|Venous Air Embolism}}</ref>。

==病理學==
若血管中有開口，且存在允許氣體進入的壓力梯度，就可能會有空氣栓塞。因為大部份動脈及靜脈的血管壓力大於大氣壓力，血管有傷口時不一定都會有空氣栓塞<!--In the veins above the heart, such as in the head and neck, the pressure is less than atmospheric and an injury may let air in. {{Citation needed|date=January 2011}} This is one reason why [[surgeon|surgeon]]s must be particularly careful when operating on the [[brain|brain]], and why the head of the bed is tilted down when inserting or removing a [[central_venous_catheter|central venous catheter]] from the [[jugular_vein|jugular]] or [[subclavian_vein|subclavian vein]]s. {{Citation needed|date=December 2010}}-->。若空氣進入靜脈，會到心臟的右側，然後進入肺部<ref>Emergency Medical Responder 3rd Can Ed. Pearson, 2010 pp.45</ref><!-- This can cause the vessels of the lung to constrict, raising the pressure in the right side of the heart{{Citation needed|date=April 2011}}.-->。若血管中的壓力夠大，而且患者有心臟卵圓孔未閉的問題，氣泡可能會跑到心臟的左側，甚至進入腦部或是[[冠狀動脈|冠狀動脈]]<!--{{Citation needed|date=December 2010}}-->，這是最危險的空氣栓塞情形。

<!--[[physical_trauma|Trauma]] to the lung can also cause an air embolism. This may happen after a patient is placed on a [[ventilator|ventilator]] and air is forced into an injured vein or artery, causing sudden death. {{Citation needed|date=January 2011}} -->在[[潛水|潛水]]時閉氣上昇可能會因為壓力差，強迫肺中的空氣進入肺動脈或是靜脈中<ref name=emr474>Emergency Medical Responder 3rd Can Ed. Pearson, 2010 pp.474</ref>。
空氣進入血管可能是無意中造成的，也可能是有意的。像不正確的使用[[注射器|注射器]]，或是沒有仔細的將血液透析迴路的空氣先排出<ref name="Emby 2012" />。<!-- and [[industrial_injury|industrial injury]] resulting from use of [[compressed_air|compressed air]].{{citation needed|reason=The source given is extremely dubious|date=March 2016}}<ref name="The Joy Of Sex">{{cite book|last1=Comfort|first1=Alan|title=The Joy Of Sex|date=2003|publisher=Simon and Schuster|isbn=9780743477741|page=228|accessdate=17 January 2016}}</ref> However, the amount of air that would be administered by a single small syringe is, in most cases, not enough to suddenly stop the heart, nor cause instant death.{{Citation needed|date=April 2010}} However, such bubbles may occasionally reach the arterial system through a [[patent_foramen_ovale|patent foramen ovale]], as noted above, and cause random [[ischemic|ischemic]] damage, depending on their route of arterial travel. {{Citation needed|date=December 2010}}-->

有出現過空氣由子宮或是女性生殖器傷口進入血管中，造成空氣栓塞的案例，但此情形相當少見<ref name=Kaiser>{{cite journal |last1=Kaiser |first1=RT |year=1994 |title=Air embolism death of a pregnant woman secondary to orogenital sex |journal=Academic Emergency Medicine |volume=6 |issue=1 |pages=555–558 |doi=10.1111/j.1553-2712.1994.tb02552.x}}</ref><ref name=Marc>{{cite journal |last1=Marc |first1=B |last2=Chadly |first2=A |last3=Durigon |first3=M |year=1990 |title=Fatal air embolism during female autoerotic practice |journal=International Journal of Legal Medicine |volume=104 |issue=1 |pages=59–61 |publisher=Springer Berlin / Heidelberg |doi=10.1007/BF01816487 |pmid=11453096}}</ref>，若是懷孕的女性，其空氣栓塞的風險更大<ref name=Kaiser />。也有案例是為了要墮胎，自行注射空氣，因此出現空氣栓塞<ref name=Marc /><!--These appear to have been due to damage to the placenta allowing air to enter the bloodstream.-->除了孕婦外，未懷孕的婦女也可能有空氣栓塞的情形，至少有一個案例是女性在自慰時將物體放進陰道中，因此造成空氣栓塞<ref>name=Marc>{{cite journal |last1=Marc |first1=B |last2=Chadly |first2=A |last3=Durigon |first3=M |year=1990 |title=Fatal air embolism during female autoerotic practice |journal=International Journal of Legal Medicine |volume=104 |issue=1 |pages=59–61 |publisher=Springer Berlin / Heidelberg |doi=10.1007/BF01816487 |pmid=11453096}}</ref>。有案例是在性行為中對孕婦陰部吹氣，後來出現空氣栓塞，後來死亡<!--<ref name="The Joy Of Sex"/>{{citation needed|reason=The source given is extremely dubious|date=March 2016}}--><ref name=Kaiser/>。

==治療==
心臟中較大的氣泡（可能是因為傷口，使得空氣可以進入較大的血管中）會持續性的出現機械式[[心雜音|心雜音]]。此時需將病人維持{{le|頭下腳上姿勢|Trendelenburg position}}<!--{{Dubious|reason=See [[Trendelenburg_position|Trendelenburg position]] for dissenting PoV|date=July 2011}}-->，並且維持左側臥位。頭下腳上姿勢可以讓左心室氣泡離開冠狀動脈竇口（主動脈瓣附近），避免氣泡進入冠狀動脈（會導致中風）。<!--Left lateral decubitus positioning helps to trap air in the non-dependent segment of the right ventricle (where it is more likely to remain instead of progressing into the pulmonary artery and occluding it).-->左側臥位也避免氣泡透過未閉的卵圓孔（約30%成人有此問題）進入左心室，造成遠端動脈的空氣栓塞症狀<ref name=CMBI /><ref>Brunicardi, F. Schwartz's Principles of Surgery, 9th Ed, McGraw Hill, 2009. p. 144</ref>。

動脈空氣栓塞及靜脈空氣栓塞建議用高壓氧進行治療。這是為了避免局部缺血，也加速氣泡的縮小<ref name="Emby 2012" />。

<!--For venous air embolism the Trendelenburg or left lateral positioning of a patient with an air-lock obstruction of the right ventricle may move the air bubble in the ventricle and allow blood flow under the bubble.<ref>Raskin JM, Benjamine E, Iberti TJ. (1985)''Venous air embolism: Case report and review.'' Mt Sinai J Med. 1985;52:367.</ref>
-->
若患者出現動脈空氣栓塞的臨床症狀，建議進行100%的純氧治療，可以使移除氣泡中的氮氣，也增加組織的含氧量。特別建議用在心肺或神經系統受損的情況下，早期處理的效果最好，若受傷後三十小時以內接受治療，都還是有效果<ref name="Emby 2012" />。

===併發症===
若是因為遲發性[[腦水腫|腦水腫]]，進行[[高壓氧治療|高壓氧治療]]，之後往往是空氣栓塞的高發期<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Pearson|first1=RR|last2=Goad|first2=RF|title=Delayed cerebral edema complicating cerebral arterial gas embolism: case histories.|journal=Undersea biomedical research|date=December 1982|volume=9|issue=4|pages=283–96|pmid=7168093}}</ref>。

==植物界==
空氣栓塞也會出現在[[維管束植物|維管束植物]]的[[木质部|木质部]]，原因是因為[[空穴現象|空穴現象]]造成的{{le|導水率|Hydraulic conductivity}}。導水率下降的原因可能包括水的應力以及凍融循環等因素。

植物中也有許多機制以避免空氣栓塞，包括在植物不同部位的{{le|維管細胞|Vessel element}}長度及直徑的變化，以及透過關閉葉片上的[[气孔|气孔]]來減少蒸发作用。

